'''Shirayama-hime Shrine''' (白山比咩神社) is a {{ill|shrine|ja|神社|12=draft|12=draft}} in Japan.
* {{ill|Shirayama Hime Shrine|ja|白山比咩神社|12=draft|12=draft}} - Located in {{ill|Hakusan|ja|白山市|12=draft|12=draft}}, {{ill|Ishikawa Prefecture|ja|石川県|12=draft|12=draft}}, in Sannomiya-chō. The head shrine of all {{ill|Hakusan Shrines|ja|白山神社|12=draft|12=draft}} in Japan. * {{ill|Shirayama-hime Shrine (Ena)|ja|白山比咩神社 (恵那市)|12=draft|12=draft}} - Located in {{ill|Ena|ja|恵那市|12=draft|12=draft}}, {{ill|Gifu Prefecture|ja|岐阜県|12=draft|12=draft}}. * {{ill|Shirayama-hime Shrine (Takaoka)|ja|白山比咩神社 (高岡市)|12=draft|12=draft}} - Located in {{ill|Takaoka|ja|高岡市|12=draft|12=draft}}, {{ill|Toyama Prefecture|ja|富山県|12=draft|12=draft}}, in Ejiri. * {{ill|Shirayama-hime Shrine (Tsu Ichishi-chō Iō)|ja|白山比咩神社 (津市一志町井生)|12=draft|12=draft}} - Located in {{ill|Tsu|ja|津市|12=draft|12=draft}}, {{ill|Mie Prefecture|ja|三重県|12=draft|12=draft}}, in Ichishi-chō Iō. * {{ill|Shirayama-hime Shrine (Tsu Hakusan-chō Kawaguchi)|ja|白山比咩神社 (津市白山町川口)|12=draft|12=draft}} - Located in Tsu, Mie Prefecture, in Hakusan-chō Kawaguchi. * {{ill|Shirayama-hime Shrine (Tsu Hakusan-chō Minamide)|ja|白山比咩神社 (津市白山町南出)|12=draft|12=draft}} - Located in Tsu, Mie Prefecture, in Hakusan-chō Minamide. * {{ill|Shirayama-hime Shrine (Tsu Hakusan-chō Yamadano)|ja|白山比咩神社 (津市白山町山田野)|12=draft|12=draft}} - Located in Tsu, Mie Prefecture, in Hakusan-chō Yamadano. * {{ill|Shirayama-hime Shrine (Nishinomiya)|ja|白山姫神社 (西宮市)|12=draft|12=draft}} - Located in {{ill|Nishinomiya|ja|西宮市|12=draft|12=draft}}, {{ill|Hyōgo Prefecture|ja|兵庫県|12=draft|12=draft}}, in Kozone-chō. * {{ill|Shirayama-hime Shrine (Iwakuni)|ja|白山比咩神社 (岩国市)|12=draft|12=draft}} - Located in {{ill|Iwakuni|ja|岩国市|12=draft|12=draft}}, {{ill|Yamaguchi Prefecture|ja|山口県|12=draft|12=draft}}, in Yokoyama.
{{Aimai}}
